Package it.polimi.ingsw.network.message

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardMessage
    Message which contains the board.
    BuildMessage
    Message which contains the positions available for the building phase.
    ColorsMessage
    Message which contains the colors available or the color picked from a user.
    DisconnectionMessage
    Message to notify a disconnection to the other players.
    ErrorMessage
    Message to notify an error to the user.
    GenericMessage
    Message to notify generic information to the user.
    GodListMessage
    Message which contains the gods available or the god picked from a user.
    LobbyMessage
    Message which contains the current players and the maximum size of the lobby .
    LoginReply
    Message used to confirm or discard a login request of a client.
    LoginRequest
    Message used by the client to request a login to the server.
    MatchInfoMessage
    Message which contains information about the current status of the match.
    Message
    Abstract message class which must be extended by each message type.
    PingMessage
    Message used to keep the connection alive.
    PlayerNumberReply
    Message used to send to the server the number of players picked by the client.
    PlayerNumberRequest
    Message used to ask the client the maximum number of players of the game.
    PositionMessage
    Message which contains a list of positions.
    PrepareEffectMessage
    Message used to notify the preparation phase of a god's effect.
    WinMessage
    Message to notify that a player has won the game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MessageType
    This enum contains all the message type available and used by the server and clients.
